If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
